    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR. This specimen features the legendary 4G63 inline-four with MIVEC technology, paired with a factory-original twin-scroll turbocharger for optimal volumetric efficiency. The 6-speed close-ratio gearbox provides surgical engagement, while the Active Center Differential (ACD) and helical front limited-slip differential remain in peak operating condition. The chassis is supported by factory Bilstein monotube dampers and lightweight BBS forged wheels. Free from typical performance-car fatigue, this Evo maintains its factory-spec structural rigidity and pristine mechanical tolerances. A rare, unmolested example of Japanese engineering excellence for the discerning collector.",
