      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh exterior with a deep, glass-like luster\u2014entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather bolsters show zero signs of wear, the original carpets are pristine, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history from day one with all preventative maintenance performed by certified technicians. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car performs exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Includes all original keys, window sticker, and owner's manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, investment-grade vehicle.",
